title: Important Keybinds for Qutebrowser
tags: @zettel _method qutebrowser
roam-id: 95ff79c9-fb39-4cd2-9232-efdc6b28342e
type: text/markdown

shortcut   functionality
  ---------- --------------------------------------
  g t        fuzzy find tab and select with enter
  g C        clone current tab to right
  yyPp       clone current tab with favicon
  g J/K      move tab right or left
  yy         copy page url
  yT         copy page title
